These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-1::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, davidoff, fonseca, old-henry, blend, dunhill, montecristo
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: june, july, november, april, may, january, february
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is the havana-smoker##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is the old-henry-smoker##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is in the middle##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the fonseca-smoker is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
11. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
12. the fonseca-smoker is the person who's birthday is in may##1
13. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
14. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |    7    |
| Cigar   | blend      | fonseca      | dunhill    | montecristo    | davidoff | havana     | old-henry     |
| Birthday   | april | may | november | june | january   | february | july |

