.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: azalea, iris, begonia, daisy, rose, amaryllis, marigold
The people have 7 different hobbies: magic-tricks, skydiving, woodworking, fishing, cooking, dancing, gardening
 1. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
 5. the person who growsrose is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who growsdaisy##1
 7. the person who growsiris is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 8. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 9. the person who growsdaisy is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
10. the person who growsbegonia is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who growsiris##2
11. the person who growsamaryllis is in the middle##1
12. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left or far right##3
13. the person who growsiris is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |    3    |     4      |      5      |     6     |   7    |
| Flower   | iris   | begonia | daisy | amaryllis   | marigold | azalea | rose |
| Hobby           | cooking | magic-tricks          | dancing    | skydiving | fishing     | woodworking      | gardening    |

