.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-3::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: helicopter, bus, taxi, skateboard, motorbike, ship, boat
There are 7 different nationalities: thai, japanese, colombian, russian, french, american, british
 1. the colombian is on the right of the british##1
 2. the british is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
 3. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the thai##3
 4. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the ship and the person driving the skateboard##2
 5. the american is on the left or right of the japanese##3
 6. the colombian is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the french is in an odd position##4
 8. the thai is on the far left##1
 9. the japanese is the person driving the helicopter##1
10. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1
11. the american is the person driving the boat##1
12. the french is between the person driving the taxi and the person driving the boat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |       5        |        6        |     7      |
| Transport   | skateboard        | bus  | ship | taxi | motorbike           | boat           | helicopter  |
| Nationality    | thai | russian | british   | colombian    | french | american | japanese |

