 3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person traveling to miami is in an even position##4
 6. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
 7. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
10. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
11. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
12. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left##1
13. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4      |      5       |      6      |      7      |
| City   | berlin | prague    | edinburgh | miami | hannover      | rome | nizza |
| Movie-Genre     | time-travel  | animation | sports   | epic  | action | family     | horror    |

