 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
 5. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching comedy movies and the person watching crime movies##2
 6. the person driving the skateboard is in an even position##4
 7. the person watching drama movies is the person driving the car##1
 8. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
 9. the person driving the airplane is in the middle##1
10. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
11. the person watching mystery movies is in an even position##4
12. the person driving the helicopter is in an odd position##4
13. the person driving the tram is the person watching documentary movies##1
14. the person watching drama movies is on the far left##1
15. the person watching drama movies is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

