 3. the person playing bridge is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 5. the person who likes black is in an odd position##4
 6. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4
 7. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
 8. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person who likes ebony##3
 9. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
10. the person playing chess is the person who likes brown##1
11. the person playing backgammon is between the person playing canasta and the person who likes ebony##2

.:: Answer ::.
