.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-18::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: march, february, may, june, september, august, december
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: scientific, thriller, superhero, crime, action, disaster, animation
 1. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
 2. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
 3. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 6. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is in an even position##4
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
 9. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person watching crime movies and the person who's birthday is in august##2
11. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
12. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |     2     |    3     |   4   |    5    |       6       |      7      |
| Birthday   | september     | august   | december      | may | february    | june | march |
| Movie-Genre       | superhero | thriller | action | crime  | animation | scientific     | disaster    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-19::.
City: colone, marseilles, boston, london, nizza, liverpool, venice
There are 7 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, juice, milk, mirinda, sprite, tea
 1. the person traveling to marseilles is the person drinking sprite##1
 2. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
 3. the person drinking mirinda is the person traveling to venice##1
 4. the person drinking tea is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 5. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
 7. the person traveling to london is in an odd position##4
 8. the person traveling to nizza is the person drinking juice##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
10. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
11. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
12. the person traveling to london is in an odd position##4
13. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
14. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |     5     |    6    |    7    |
| City          | london  | marseilles | colone     | venice  | boston | liverpool    | nizza  |
| Beverage   | milk | sprite  | lemonade | mirinda | hot-chocolate | tea | juice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-20::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: trike, bike, jet-ski, airplane, tram, subway, taxi
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: surfing, weightlifting, climbing, cycling, basketball, ice-hockey, tennis
 1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 2. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
 3. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
 4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the airplane is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 8. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 9. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
10. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
11. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
12. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |   5    |      6      |    7     |
| Transport          | subway   | jet-ski | taxi | trike | tram | bike | airplane |
| Sport   | basketball | tennis      | ice-hockey     | climbing  | cycling | surfing         | weightlifting    |

 